[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rio Olympics 2016: Briton Sally Conway wins -70kg judo bronze

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Briton Sally Conway defeated Austria's Bernadette Graf to win the -70kg judo bronze medal.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
